{"tid":583533,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過訂做組合床？","createTime":"2018-03-07T05:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T09:20:06.000Z","uid":64129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"856f8ddd95b7aec119154b3b2218a9ed770574d8","tid":583533,"uid":64129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"想要果種上面床下面電腦枱<br />\n但因為想張床比平時果種大<br />\n（大約正常人可以攤開哂手咁闊）<br />\n同埋張枱可以深啲 放多啲野<br />\n同埋唔要平時放keyboard果行<br />\n可以多啲legroom<br />\n櫃果d其實唔洗點要咁得<br />\n<br />\n想問下大約要幾錢同埋有乜邊間推薦？<br />\nbudget 8000內到有冇可能做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a23381bb8d61bc2f96f1ec875e7cf808825087b","tid":583533,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人斬到成頸血都唔去ikea"},{"pid":"b9457510e0cfe3f628dbe4ebc684d5980fbb3ba0","tid":583533,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"之前有個fd試過用4千蚊訂張木架床(比標準size大), 然後用2千5左右去宜家自己搵枱搵櫃放入去"},{"pid":"3ece296867c56ebac542cd98fc634cb0739f748b","tid":583533,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"訓緊，整咗6千，去傢俬鋪講你個idea佢就會報到大約個價比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我下層係書枱＋衣櫃"},{"pid":"ea4fcdf986b64c22a7f694ed8ea8e7bb23a5ee3f","tid":583533,"uid":14548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:20:06.000Z","msg":"我傢私鋪訂造過 六千幾，夾板黎，唔係好穩陣，你最好叫佢加厚d板<br />\n<br />\n不過訓左一年都頂唔順換返普通枱加床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上床下枱好睇唔好用，除非你新私樓超高樓底，床底可以成個人行入去，唔係起身又驚撞頭，加上要爬上爬落唔夠直接可以訓上咁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}